data.description: This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sits on a private lot with abundant gardens, a two-car garage and separate building with the possibility to create a detached office, in-law cottage or workshop! The spacious open living room – dining room has vaulted ceilings and sliders out to a large screened paver lanai with an oversized hot tub. The kitchen features granite counters, a natural stone backsplash and a pantry cabinet. The primary suite has vaulted ceilings, a closet system, tile shower and an attached storage room. Two more bedrooms share a full bathroom with a natural stone accent wall. There are many possibilities for the spacious lot, which has mature landscaping and a separate screened enclosure. Conveniently located in close proximity to shopping, hospitals, schools and universities, highways and more!
